{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_04_03",
  "title": "川咲さくら 3話 みんなー！　この指とーまれ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ミュージックビデオ撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Music Video Shooting Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ撮影が始まるぞ。準備はいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's about to start shooting soon. Are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　いつでもいけます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Anytime!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2366.6667381,
          "startTime": 8.6333334048
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても凄い歓声ですね。急に決まった\nライブなのにこんなに人が集まるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's impressive. Even though this live was decided suddenly‚\nso many people have gathered…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "サニピを応援してる人がそれだけいるってことだ\nこの歓声はさくら達が頑張ってきた結果だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because there are so many people here to support Sunny Peace.\nThis cheering is the result of Sakura and Sunny Peace's hard work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n今回の撮影では無理を言ってすみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nI'm sorry for making a difficult request for this shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYと同じ会場でライブをするなんて\n準備は大変でしたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think that we could perform a live at a venue like I-UNITY\nYou must have worked hard because of the preparations‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんとか会場の使用許可が下りて良かったよ\nそれにしてもあの時のさくらには驚いたな――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're fortunate that we somehow managed to get permission to use the venue from the president.\nBy the way‚ I was really surprised by Sakura back then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\n私、MVのアイデアを思いついちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san\nI just had an idea for a music video.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "この会場にファンのみんなを集めて\nライブをするんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We gather all our fans at this venue\nand hold a live concert!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYで私達が歌った時\n私達とファンのみんなの心は確かに繋がっていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we sang on I-UNITY‚\nour hearts were truly connected with the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "あの時の一体感をMVでも表現出来れば、サニピを\n見たことがない人達とも、想いを繋げられるはずです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we can express that unity in the MV‚\nwe can connect with people who have never seen Sunny Peace before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、ライブを撮影してMVにするのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ shooting the live concert for the MV…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "新曲で『この指とまれ、隣の笑顔、寂しい顔も\n繋がればほら幸せ』って歌詞があるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are lyrics in our new song‚ \"Come here and get closer‚\nthe smile next door‚ even the lonely faces‚ when connected‚ see the happiness.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "人が集まって、心が一つになって、想いが繋がって\nみんなが幸せになる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "People come together‚ hearts become one‚\nemotions connect‚ and everyone becomes happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "そんな曲に込めた想いを表現するには\n私達のライブを見てもらうのが一番いいと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To express the feelings we've put into the song‚\nI think it's best to show them our live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "あ……でも、やっぱり難しいかな……\nMVのために会場を押さえてライブするなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… but‚ maybe it's too difficult…\nReserving a venue for a live concert just for an MV…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、やっぱりいいです！\nただの思いつきなので今のは忘れて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ never mind!\nPlease forget what I just said. It just corssed my mind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらはそうするのが一番いいと思ったんだろ？\nだったら取り消す必要はない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ do you think that's the best way?\nThen there's no need to take it back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "出来ないなんて決めつけないで胸を張って提案してくれ\nその想いを実現させるのが俺達スタッフの仕事だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't assume you can't do it; confidently propose it.\nIt's our job as staff to make those dreams come true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n私はこの場所でMVを撮りたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nI want to shoot the MV in this place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYは今の私達に出来る\n最高のステージだったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-UNITY was the best stage for now\nthat we can perform…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "あの時のパフォーマンスを出来る限り再現して\n会場に来られなかった人達にも届けたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to recreate that performance as much as possible\nand reach the people who couldn't come to the venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "この歌で私達と、会場にいるファンの人達と\nMVを見てくれるみんなの心を繋げてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this song‚ we'll connect the hearts of us‚\nthe fans in the venue‚ and those watching the MV!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
