      "text": "よくみんなが「サニピの歌から元気をもらった」って\n言ってくれるけど、それは私達も同じです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Many of you often say that you get energy from Sunny Peace's songs‚\nbut the same goes for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
