      "text": "私達はファンのみんなから元気をもらってます\nみんなの応援が私達のエネルギーです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We get strength from all of you‚ our fans.\nWe get energy from everyone's support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
