      "text": "私達五人と応援してくれるみんな……バラバラだった\nピースが繋がって、どこまでも広がっていく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Five of us and our fans were……all scattered at first‚\nbut the pieces connected and spread endlessly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
