      "text": "そんなみんなとの絆を表現したくて\nこんな形でMVを撮影したいって提案しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to express that bond with everyone\nand that's why I proposed shooting the MV like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr030.m4a",
      "text": "この曲はみんなの想いを乗せて\nどこまでも広がっていける力強い曲だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This song carries everyone's feelings‚\nand it's a powerful song that can spread endlessly…",
        "id": ""
      },
