    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr031.m4a",
      "text": "みんなもサニピの大事な欠片だよ！　私達の歌で\n笑顔になってくれた、みんながサニーピースだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone is also a precious piece of Sunny Peace!\nPeople who made smiles with our songs are all Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr032.m4a",
      "text": "私達はこれからも旅を続けます！\nみんなと一緒にもっと遠くへ！　もっと高くへ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll continue our journey!\nTogether with everyone‚ farther and higher!",
